# Aegis SIEM

> Lightweight Security Information & Event Management tool with a novel **ATRS** (Adaptive Threat Risk Score) algorithm — built for real macOS system log telemetry.

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Activate virtual environment
source .venv/bin/activate

# 2. Start the dashboard
python dashboard/app.py

# 3. Open in browser
open http://127.0.0.1:5001
```

The dashboard auto-collects real macOS authentication logs on startup (ASL, wtmp, Unified Log).

## Install As A Tool (No Manual Clone)

Anyone can install Aegis directly from terminal:

```bash
python3 -m pip install --upgrade "git+https://github.com/zeehawww/siem.git"
```

Then run it from anywhere:

```bash
aegis help
aegis analyze
aegis status
aegis srtc
aegis serve
```

If `aegis` command is not found, add user bin to PATH (macOS):

```bash
export PATH="$HOME/Library/Python/3.*/bin:$PATH"
```

Or use:

```bash
python3 -m pip install --user "git+https://github.com/zeehawww/siem.git"
```

## Navigation

| Page | Route | Description |
